<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Password Reset</title>
  <style>
    /* General Reset */
    body, html {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      width: 100%;
      font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background-color: #f4f4f7;
    }
    a {
      text-decoration: none;
    }
    /* Container */
    .email-wrapper {
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background-color: #ffffff;
      padding: 40px 20px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(0,0,0,0.05);
    }
    /* Header */
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 24px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: #333333;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    /* Body text */
    .content {
      font-size: 16px;
      color: #555555;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    /* Reset button */
    .reset-button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #5b63f7;
      color: #ffffff !important;
      font-weight: bold;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 6px;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-align: center;
    }
    /* Footer */
    .footer {
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #999999;
      text-align: center;
      margin-top: 40px;
    }
    /* Responsive */
    @media screen and (max-width: 480px) {
      .email-wrapper {
        padding: 30px 15px;
      }
      .header {
        font-size: 20px;
      }
      .reset-button {
        padding: 12px 18px;
        font-size: 14px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="email-wrapper">
    <div class="header">
      Reset Your Password
    </div>
    <div class="content">
      You recently requested to reset your password for your account <strong>{{email}}</strong>. Click the button below to reset it. <br><br>
      This password reset link is valid for <strong>1 hour</strong> only. If you did not request a password reset, please ignore this email.
    </div>
    <div style="text-align:center;">
      <a href="https://your-app-domain.com/reset-password?token={{resetToken}}" class="reset-button">
        Reset Password
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="content" style="margin-top:20px;">
      Or copy and paste this token into the app manually:<br>
      <code style="display:block; margin-top:8px; font-size:16px; background:#f1f1f1; padding:8px 12px; border-radius:4px;">{{resetToken}}</code>
    </div>
    <div class="footer">
      If you didnâ€™t request this, please ignore this email. <br>
      &copy; 2025 YourApp. All rights reserved.
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
